The number of times that we visit a dentist over years has risen considerably thanks to our insensitivity to cleaner teeth. Not because we do not brush but because we do not brush the right way with the right brush. Revolutionary cleaning for your teeth comes with this electric brush.

Oscillates at 6000 Circles Per Minute for Vigorous Cleaning of Teeth
For the kind of lifestyle we all live with aerated drinks and smoking such close friends this brush brings vigorous cleaning for cleaner and whiter teeth. The DUPONT nylon bristles on the head treat your teeth with utmost care as the brush oscillates at 6000 circles per minute.

Changeable Head
Hygiene is very important and this brush maintains that. You have three different interchangeable heads to ensure more members of the family can use the brush but with a different colored head.

Waterproof
The mechanism of the electric brush is made with a waterproof body to ensure durability and better cleaning.

Safe to Use
As scary as an electric toothbrush may sound this particular construct is safe to be used by all age groups and ensures to not leave any damage behind.

CE ROHS LFGB FDA Approved
To further ensure safety the brush is declared to have met all appropriate provisions of relevant regions and certification from various health concern boards to reassure absolute safety is promised.
